<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>이<sp/>문서<sp/>`docs/text-visualizer/16-performance-optimization-analysis.ko.md`를<sp/>먼저<sp/>읽는다.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>그<sp/>다음<sp/>`docs/text-visualizer/15-current-optimization-status.ko.md`를<sp/>읽는다.</highlight></codeline>
